ania, Bronx|Morrisania]] [C]<br/>1855<ref name=French/>&ndash;1874<ref name=Law1874/>|boxstyle_Borough =background-color: #cef2e0|boxstyle_Westchester =background-color: #faf5ff|boxstyle_Farms =background-color: #faf5ff|boxstyle_Morrisania =background-color: #faf5ff}}
