{{familytree |a|a=[A] = A part of [[Montgomery County, New York|Montgomery County]] until 1791, then [[Herkimer County, New York|Herkimer County]] from 1791-1794,<br/>[[Onondaga County, New York|Onondaga County]] from 1794-1799, and [[Cayuga County, New York|Cayuga County]] from 1799 and thereafter.|boxstyle_a=background-color: #d1e231}}
